<h2>1. Where can I get a copy of the Lead Rules? </h2>
<p>To receive a copy of the Texas Environmental Lead Reduction Rules, go the to <a title="Rules page" href="/elp/laws-rules.aspx">Rules page</a> on this site, or call the DSHS at (512) 834-6787, ext. 2434, or (888) 778-9440 (toll-free in Texas). </p>

