<p>The <a title="Texas Commission on Environmental Quality (TCEQ)" href="http://www.tceq.state.tx.us/">Texas Commission on Environmental Quality (TCEQ)</a> will be able to assist you with questions about lead in water by calling the Water Supply Division at (512) 239-4691, or by calling any of the <a title="TCEQ Regional Offices" href="http://www.tceq.state.tx.us/about/directory/region/reglist.html">TCEQ Regional Offices</a>. </p>

